orking procedure using the authority given by Regulation 32 of the Citizens Investment Trust Regulations, 2048 BS.","title":"Citizens Investment Trust to provide pension service to public - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/09/126284/","video":[]}
